.rule_3_7_ensure_ip_verify_is_set_to_reverse_path_for_untrusted_interfaces

Reference: all/asa_91_firewall_config/protect_tools.html

Remediation: 
Step 1: Acquire the name of the untrusted interface <interface_name>

Step 2: Run the following command to enable protection against IP spoofing
hostname(config)# ip verify reverse-path interface <interface_name>





